&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This Vacancy is for internal applicants too UHMBT only &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a hard working, dynamic team player to join our Admin and Clerical team at Ante-natal Clinic/Gynaecology Outpatient department and Furness General Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will work Monday-Friday between the hours of 8.30am-5pm. However, two part time candidates will be considered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will provide an efficient and effective clerical service to the multi-disciplinary team and demonstrate an attitude which respects and values service users’ and their carers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will act as first point of contact for all telephone and reception enquiries, ensuring that messages are forwarded to the appropriate persons and visitors are welcomed to the department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will provide an effective clerical service to support the team, including photocopying, typing, data input and maintenance of an effective filing and retrieval system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsibility, in conjunction with other administrative staff, booking appointments and associated data entry including the retrieval and maintenance of patient records, ensuring appropriate records are maintained.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameClare JonesJob titleANC ManagerEmail addressclare.jones@mbht.nhs.ukTelephone number07790819374&lt;/p&gt;
